HEADWORD: Brachydiagonal
<hw>Brach`y*di*ag"o*nal</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>brachy`s</grk> short + E. <ets>diagonal</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Pertaining to the shorter diagonal, as of a rhombic
prism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Brachydiagonal axis</b></col>, <cd>the shorter lateral
axis of an orthorhombic crystal.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brachydiagonal</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Brachydiagonal
<hw>Brach`y*di*ag"o*nal</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The shorter of the
diagonals in a rhombic prism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brachydome</ent>⟦br⟧
